text: Lost Time is the third studio album by Seattle-based pop punk band Tacocat, released on April 1, 2016 on Hardly Art. It was produced by Erik Blood. ==Critical reception== According to review aggregator Metacritic, based on 13 critic reviews, Lost Time has a score of 76 out of 100, indicating "generally favorable reviews". ===Accolades=== {|class="sortable wikitable" |- !
